Title: Geometric Phase in Quaternionic Quantum Mechanics
Authors: M. D. Maia and V. B. Bezerra
Comments: Latex. 14 pages, no figures. Updates most of hep-th/9904067, to
  appear in the International Journal of Theoretical Physics
Journal-ref: Int.J.Theor.Phys. 40 (2001) 1283-1294
\\
  Quaternion quantum mechanics is examined at the level of unbroken SU(2) gauge
symmetry. A general quaternionic phase expression is derived from formal
properties of the quaternion algebra.
